2
00:01:30,870 --> 00:01:33,000
=Episod 25=

3
00:01:37,160 --> 00:01:37,690
Dewa agung,

4
00:01:38,280 --> 00:01:40,610
bukankah kita datang untuk
meraikan hari jadi tuan puteri?

5
00:01:41,040 --> 00:01:41,890
Mengapa tak ke sana?

6
00:01:48,930 --> 00:01:49,640
Zi Han.

7
00:01:50,720 --> 00:01:52,160
Kita dah datang ke Istana Qing Chi
untuk seketika,

8
00:01:52,970 --> 00:01:54,770
pasti ada banyak urusan di Alam Syaitan

9
00:01:55,130 --> 00:01:56,610
yang tunggu saya uruskan.

10
00:01:59,770 --> 00:02:00,690
Kita baliklah.

11
00:02:01,160 --> 00:02:02,720
Sen Jian akan uruskan hal
di Alam Syaitan.

12
00:02:03,970 --> 00:02:05,560
Kita boleh tinggal di Istana Qing Chi
untuk beberapa hari lagi.

13
00:02:09,330 --> 00:02:11,200
Wu Huan dah tahu identiti saya.

14
00:02:11,560 --> 00:02:13,290
Puak Syaitan mesti buat persediaan.

15
00:02:47,610 --> 00:02:49,440
Tuan putera bawa begini banyak
askar syurga ke Istana Qing Chi,

16
00:02:49,440 --> 00:02:50,480
apa maksud itu?

17
00:02:51,410 --> 00:02:52,880
Saya bawa edik Istana Syurga

18
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:53,970
untuk beri kepada Qing Mu.

19
00:02:54,330 --> 00:02:56,240
Pengurus Feng Ran, bolehkah saya masuk?

20
00:02:57,240 --> 00:02:58,650
Memandangkan ada edik Istana Syurga,

21
00:02:58,650 --> 00:02:59,840
sudah tentu tuan putera boleh masuk.

22
00:03:00,440 --> 00:03:01,930
Namun, menurut peraturan
Istana Qing Chi,

23
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:03,880
orang yang tak berkenaan
tak dibenarkan masuk.

24
00:03:03,880 --> 00:03:05,410
Pedati dan tandu diraja juga perlu
tunggu di luar.

25
00:03:07,690 --> 00:03:08,730
Kamu tunggu di sini.

26
00:03:09,290 --> 00:03:10,050
Ya!

27
00:03:31,880 --> 00:03:33,440
Apa tujuannya Istana Syurga suruh awak

28
00:03:33,730 --> 00:03:34,880
bawa askar ke sini?

29
00:03:35,330 --> 00:03:36,560
Berikan tekanan atau provokasi?

30
00:03:37,480 --> 00:03:39,400
Cuba buli kami kerana tiada
orang handalan di Istana Qing Chi?

31
00:03:39,600 --> 00:03:41,010
Kalau Dewa Gu Jun berada di sini,

32
00:03:41,040 --> 00:03:42,680
kamu tak dapat begitu biadab.

33
00:03:43,650 --> 00:03:44,560
Jangan marah.

34
00:03:45,120 --> 00:03:46,010
Kita bercakap di dalam.

35
00:03:46,010 --> 00:03:46,760
Saya marah.

36
00:03:49,120 --> 00:03:49,890
Saya tanya awak,

37
00:03:50,400 --> 00:03:51,370
di mana Qing Mu?

38
00:03:52,760 --> 00:03:53,680
Beritahu saya dulu,

39
00:03:53,890 --> 00:03:55,760
apa tujuan awak datang jumpa Qing Mu?

40
00:04:00,650 --> 00:04:01,290
Baik.

41
00:04:01,290 --> 00:04:02,170
Awak tak mahu cakap, betul?

42
00:04:02,450 --> 00:04:02,960
Saya akan arahkan orang

43
00:04:02,960 --> 00:04:04,600
menjolok sarang tebuan di depan pintu,

44
00:04:04,600 --> 00:04:06,290
tengok kalau-kalau askar syurga
dan panglima syurga awak dapat bertahan.

45
00:04:09,890 --> 00:04:10,930
Tuan putera membantahkah?

46
00:04:12,370 --> 00:04:13,040
Saya tak berani.

47
00:04:13,680 --> 00:04:14,930
Kalau-kalau mahu menjolok
sarang tebuan Istana Qing Chi,

48
00:04:15,290 --> 00:04:17,810
itu ialah keputusan awak.

49
00:04:18,200 --> 00:04:19,370
Awak amat bijak.

50
00:04:20,600 --> 00:04:21,730
Selepas awak lepaskan kemarahan,

51
00:04:22,120 --> 00:04:23,290
saya akan hantar salap kepada mereka

52
00:04:23,810 --> 00:04:24,810
untuk kurangkan bengkak dan kesakitan.

53
00:04:25,400 --> 00:04:27,010
Kalau kata-kata awak didapati
Permaisuri Syurga,

54
00:04:27,010 --> 00:04:28,320
siaplah awak.

55
00:04:28,680 --> 00:04:30,290
Suka hati awak.

56
00:04:31,680 --> 00:04:32,400
Sudahlah.

57
00:04:32,840 --> 00:04:35,200
Askar syurga dan panglima syurga awak
hanya laksanakan tugas mengikut arahan.

58
00:04:35,320 --> 00:04:36,530
Mereka tak patut dihukum.

59
00:04:36,600 --> 00:04:37,600
Orang yang patut dihukum

60
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:38,370
ialah awak.

61
00:04:39,250 --> 00:04:40,200
Betul.

62
00:04:40,400 --> 00:04:41,320
Selepas siapkan hal ini,

63
00:04:41,810 --> 00:04:43,480
awak boleh buat apa-apa saja
terhadap saya.

64
00:04:44,450 --> 00:04:45,450
Mulut awak

65
00:04:45,450 --> 00:04:46,400
lebih keras daripada batu.

66
00:05:14,840 --> 00:05:15,650
Ah Huan,

67
00:05:16,400 --> 00:05:17,290
apa yang awak fikir?

68
00:05:17,960 --> 00:05:20,930
Baru-baru ini, awak nampak
tak tenang hati.

69
00:05:21,650 --> 00:05:22,960
Adakah awak hadapi masalah?

70
00:05:25,320 --> 00:05:26,530
Apa lagi yang boleh saya fikir?

71
00:05:28,010 --> 00:05:29,930
Cuma fikir tentang masalah anak kita.

72
00:05:35,320 --> 00:05:36,680
Demi pertunangan Zhao'er, betul?

73
00:05:37,760 --> 00:05:39,450
Jian'er dah pergi jumpa Qing Mu.

74
00:05:40,040 --> 00:05:41,560
Hal ini mesti dapat diselesaikan.

75
00:05:43,840 --> 00:05:45,250
Macam mana kalau dia tak setuju?

76
00:05:47,280 --> 00:05:48,650
Semasa berada di Bukit Liao Wang,

77
00:05:49,530 --> 00:05:51,410
Qing Mu dan Hou Chi
bergaul dengan rapat.

78
00:05:52,690 --> 00:05:53,530
Mungkin

79
00:05:54,130 --> 00:05:55,650
dia dah ada buah hati.

80
00:05:58,480 --> 00:05:59,280
Tuanku.

81
00:06:00,040 --> 00:06:01,810
Zhao'er amat cintainya,

82
00:06:03,040 --> 00:06:04,850
tapi kalau Qing Mu tak sudi,

83
00:06:05,850 --> 00:06:07,200
biar perkara ini tamat begitu saja.

84
00:06:09,320 --> 00:06:10,690
Nampaknya, saya terlalu risau.

85
00:06:11,530 --> 00:06:12,410
Apa maksud itu?

86
00:06:13,280 --> 00:06:14,930
Qing Mu mempunyai Lembing Tai Chang.

87
00:06:15,850 --> 00:06:17,600
Kalau dia tak boleh berkhidmat
untuk Istana Syurga,

88
00:06:18,720 --> 00:06:20,280
hasrat awak untuk buka semula Alam Dewa

89
00:06:21,650 --> 00:06:23,250
mungkin tak dapat dicapai.

90
00:06:34,690 --> 00:06:35,690
Cakaplah sesuatu.

91
00:06:35,690 --> 00:06:37,040
Apa yang ingin Istana Syurga lakukan?

92
00:06:37,530 --> 00:06:38,930
Jangan-jangan kamu nak berkira

93
00:06:38,930 --> 00:06:40,130
dengan kami kerana Qing Mu

94
00:06:40,130 --> 00:06:41,320
cederakan adik awak di Bukit Liao Wang.

95
00:06:41,760 --> 00:06:42,370
Jing Jian,

96
00:06:42,760 --> 00:06:44,160
awak kawan karib Qing Mu,

97
00:06:44,160 --> 00:06:45,410
tak boleh berpaling muka.

98
00:06:48,530 --> 00:06:49,280
Feng Ran.

99
00:06:50,090 --> 00:06:50,970
Putera ngah kata,

100
00:06:51,200 --> 00:06:53,160
edik Istana Syurga adalah untuk Qing Mu.

101
00:06:53,970 --> 00:06:55,320
Memandangkan ini urusan antara mereka,

102
00:06:55,570 --> 00:06:57,200
Istana Qing Chi tak boleh campur tangan.

103
00:06:57,720 --> 00:06:59,200
Jangan buat dia rasa serba salah.

104
00:07:01,040 --> 00:07:01,720
Hou Chi.

105
00:07:02,250 --> 00:07:04,040
Memang tak elok bawa askar ke sini,

106
00:07:04,650 --> 00:07:05,970
tapi ini arahan Tuhan Ibu saya.

107
00:07:06,200 --> 00:07:07,280
Memandangkan ini arahannya,

108
00:07:07,570 --> 00:07:08,530
tak perlu cakap lagi.

109
00:07:08,880 --> 00:07:09,650
Mengenai urusannya,

110
00:07:09,850 --> 00:07:10,970
saya tak mahu dengar apa-apa pun.

111
00:07:18,370 --> 00:07:19,320
Kenapa ini?

112
00:07:20,850 --> 00:07:21,650
Tanyalah dia.

113
00:07:23,690 --> 00:07:24,970
Kami bergaul dengan baik semalam.

114
00:07:25,410 --> 00:07:26,850
Mengapa bersikap dingin hari ini?

115
00:07:27,250 --> 00:07:28,440
Siapa bergaul baik dengan dia?

116
00:07:29,760 --> 00:07:30,440
Qing Mu,

117
00:07:31,720 --> 00:07:33,130
jangan bergurau tentang perkara besar.

118
00:07:34,570 --> 00:07:35,410
Kita bercakap di tempat lain.

119
00:07:35,410 --> 00:07:36,000
Tak payah.

120
00:07:37,040 --> 00:07:38,320
Feng Ran, kita pergi ke tempat lain.

121
00:07:44,410 --> 00:07:45,570
Apa yang terjadi?

122
00:07:45,850 --> 00:07:47,000
Mengapa awak rasa begitu serba salah?

123
00:07:48,530 --> 00:07:49,720
Berterus terang saja di antara kita.

124
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:52,250
Bukannya saya tak sudi berterus terang.

125
00:07:52,690 --> 00:07:54,160
Sebab, awak takkan berjanji akan
perkara ini.

126
00:07:54,810 --> 00:07:55,930
Dewa Bapa dan Dewa Ibu saya

127
00:07:56,320 --> 00:07:58,130
ingin biar awak kuasai
tiga pasukan tentera,

128
00:07:58,410 --> 00:07:59,850
memerintah seratus ribu panglima syurga
di Istana Syurga.

129
00:08:00,570 --> 00:08:01,600
Disebabkan Lembing Tai Chang?

130
00:08:03,160 --> 00:08:03,930
Betul.

131
00:08:04,320 --> 00:08:05,130
Saya tak suka dikekang,

132
00:08:05,130 --> 00:08:05,880
awak tahu sifat saya.

133
00:08:06,690 --> 00:08:07,570
Bantu saya tolak permintaan mereka.

134
00:08:08,880 --> 00:08:10,370
Alangkah baik kalau hanya demi hal ini.

135
00:08:11,250 --> 00:08:13,930
Saya juga bawa edik Tuhan Bapa ke sini.

136
00:08:14,880 --> 00:08:16,090
Dia suruh saya datang ke Istana Qing Chi

137
00:08:19,130 --> 00:08:20,440
untuk kurniakan perkahwinan
kepada awak dan Jing Zhao.

138
00:08:21,370 --> 00:08:22,040
Apa yang awak cakap?

139
00:08:22,760 --> 00:08:23,880
Awak tahu bahawa saya dan Hou Chi...

140
00:08:24,410 --> 00:08:25,130
Qing Mu.

141
00:08:26,410 --> 00:08:27,320
Jangan berangsang.

142
00:08:27,810 --> 00:08:29,200
Sudah tentu saya tahu isi hati awak,

143
00:08:30,600 --> 00:08:31,690
tapi hal ini...

144
00:08:33,200 --> 00:08:34,690
Hal ini perlu utamakan kebaikan
untuk semua pihak.

145
00:08:35,480 --> 00:08:36,720
Semasa berada di Bukit Liao Wang
hari itu,

146
00:08:37,040 --> 00:08:38,160
kudrat dewa awak

147
00:08:38,280 --> 00:08:39,760
dirasuk sisa roh Dewa Sejati,

148
00:08:40,320 --> 00:08:42,160
tapi awak tetap cederakan
saya dan Jing Zhao.

149
00:08:42,970 --> 00:08:44,970
Pertama sekali, Istana Syurga
kehilangan air muka.

150
00:08:45,440 --> 00:08:46,160
Kedua,

151
00:08:46,250 --> 00:08:48,000
orang lain akan mengesyaki niat awak
terhadap Istana Syurga.

152
00:08:48,880 --> 00:08:49,690
Ketiga,

153
00:08:50,200 --> 00:08:51,320
awak tinggal di Istana Qing Chi.

154
00:08:51,850 --> 00:08:54,600
Oleh itu, mereka cuba mengikat saya
dengan pertunangan ini?

155
00:08:57,130 --> 00:08:59,370
Dewa Bapa dan Dewa Ibu saya kata,

156
00:08:59,370 --> 00:09:00,720
mereka ingin ajak awak ke Istana Syurga,

157
00:09:01,600 --> 00:09:04,320
tapi mereka suruh askar
ikut saya ke sini.

158
00:09:04,570 --> 00:09:05,530
Niat mereka

159
00:09:05,880 --> 00:09:07,440
mungkin bukan saja
kurniakan perkahwinan.

160
00:09:09,200 --> 00:09:10,250
Untuk menakutkan Istana Qing Chi?

161
00:09:12,280 --> 00:09:13,200
Kalau awak tak berjanji,

162
00:09:14,720 --> 00:09:15,480
mungkin...

163
00:09:19,130 --> 00:09:20,280
Istana Syurga paksa orang
dengan kekerasan.

164
00:09:21,040 --> 00:09:22,320
Kelak, masalah takkan berhenti timbul.

165
00:09:23,370 --> 00:09:24,760
Saya berseorangan, tak apa,

166
00:09:25,160 --> 00:09:26,440
tapi Dewa Gu Jun tak berada di sini.

167
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:28,690
Hou Chi tinggal di
Istana Qing Chi berseorangan.

168
00:09:29,320 --> 00:09:30,160
Pasti dia hadapi masalah.

169
00:09:33,160 --> 00:09:34,200
Saya pergi ke istana bersama awak

170
00:09:34,600 --> 00:09:35,440
untuk selesaikan hal ini.

171
00:09:35,880 --> 00:09:36,570
Baik.

172
00:09:50,040 --> 00:09:52,440
Qing Mu, awak betul-betul mahu
berahsia dengan Hou Chi

173
00:09:52,650 --> 00:09:53,600
dan pergi tanpa beritahu diakah?

174
00:09:54,040 --> 00:09:55,530
Tak boleh biar Hou Chi tahu perkara ini.

175
00:09:55,690 --> 00:09:56,650
Saya perlu pergi dan balik dengan cepat

176
00:09:56,850 --> 00:09:57,810
untuk tolak pertunangan ini.

177
00:09:58,440 --> 00:09:59,200
Qing Mu!

178
00:10:02,480 --> 00:10:03,370
Saya dah tahu.

179
00:10:04,130 --> 00:10:05,690
Saya terdengar perbualan
awak dan Jing Jian.

180
00:10:06,480 --> 00:10:07,130
Jangan risau.

181
00:10:07,480 --> 00:10:08,690
Saya takkan kahwini Jing Zhao.

182
00:10:08,930 --> 00:10:11,130
Saya akan pergi ke Istana Syurga, tolak
pengurniaan perkahwinan Raja Syurga.

183
00:10:12,040 --> 00:10:12,770
Kemudian?

184
00:10:13,210 --> 00:10:13,960
Kemudian?

185
00:10:14,330 --> 00:10:15,570
Kemudian, sudah tentu
balik ke Istana Qing Chi

186
00:10:15,690 --> 00:10:16,720
untuk lindungi dan temani awak.

187
00:10:16,720 --> 00:10:17,450
Saya takkan tinggalkan awak.

188
00:10:18,370 --> 00:10:19,960
Awak tahu hal ini rumit.

189
00:10:20,810 --> 00:10:21,960
Kita baru bercinta.

190
00:10:21,960 --> 00:10:23,250
Saya rasa berat hati
untuk biar awak pergi.

191
00:10:23,370 --> 00:10:25,450
Namun, saya tak ingin nampak
nyawa awak terancam.

192
00:10:26,330 --> 00:10:27,130
Awak mesti berhati-hati

193
00:10:27,130 --> 00:10:28,370
di Istana Syurga kali ini.

194
00:10:29,010 --> 00:10:29,720
Raja Syurga hanya

195
00:10:29,720 --> 00:10:31,210
mahu Lembing Tai Chang awak.

196
00:10:31,690 --> 00:10:32,480
Mengenai pengurniaan perkahwinan,

197
00:10:32,480 --> 00:10:33,570
dia tak dapat paksa awak.

198
00:10:33,720 --> 00:10:35,370
Perbuatannya tak berbeza dengan
penyamun di Alam Bawah.

199
00:10:35,720 --> 00:10:36,890
Namun, perlu berwaspada
terhadap segala-galanya.

200
00:10:37,370 --> 00:10:38,480
Kalau dia ingin cederakan awak,

201
00:10:39,010 --> 00:10:39,810
jangan awak bertindak melulu.

202
00:10:40,130 --> 00:10:40,930
Saya akan selesaikan segala-galanya.

203
00:10:41,930 --> 00:10:42,810
Percakapan ini

204
00:10:43,330 --> 00:10:45,130
tak macam yang dikatakan Dewi Hou Chi

205
00:10:45,130 --> 00:10:45,930
yang tak sukai saya selama ini.

206
00:10:49,080 --> 00:10:49,640
Selain itu,

207
00:10:50,330 --> 00:10:51,210
apabila awak pergi ke Istana Syurga,

208
00:10:51,210 --> 00:10:52,210
tak boleh tengok Jing Zhao,

209
00:10:52,210 --> 00:10:53,570
juga tak boleh bercakap dengannya.

210
00:10:54,600 --> 00:10:55,690
Sekarang, awak orang saya.

211
00:10:58,250 --> 00:11:00,480
Kalau ada sebarang desas-desus
tentang soal cinta,

212
00:11:00,930 --> 00:11:02,010
siaplah awak.

213
00:11:02,370 --> 00:11:03,040
Sudah tentu.

214
00:11:04,250 --> 00:11:05,840
Saya bukan saja takkan tengok Jing Zhao,

215
00:11:06,080 --> 00:11:08,250
malah, takkan tengok perempuan lain.

216
00:11:16,010 --> 00:11:17,600
Bila kamu berdua bercinta?

217
00:11:20,250 --> 00:11:21,370
Saya tumpang gembira pada kamu.

218
00:11:23,210 --> 00:11:23,840
Hou Chi,

219
00:11:24,210 --> 00:11:25,690
awak dan Qing Mu cintai satu sama lain.

220
00:11:26,330 --> 00:11:27,330
Saya berasa iri hati.

221
00:11:27,690 --> 00:11:28,370
Jangan risau.

222
00:11:28,810 --> 00:11:29,720
Kali ini pergi ke Istana Syurga,

223
00:11:30,250 --> 00:11:31,370
saya mesti lindungi Qing Mu,

224
00:11:31,640 --> 00:11:32,480
ingatkannya dalam segala-galanya,

225
00:11:32,840 --> 00:11:34,480
bantu dia beritahu Dewa Bapa
tentang isi hatinya.

226
00:11:35,570 --> 00:11:36,480
Terima kasih, tuan putera.

227
00:11:37,370 --> 00:11:38,570
Jangan panggil dia tuan putera.

228
00:11:38,690 --> 00:11:39,770
Panggil namanya saja.

229
00:11:44,250 --> 00:11:45,010
Jangan risau.

230
00:11:45,010 --> 00:11:45,890
Saya akan balik dengan cepat.

231
00:11:47,130 --> 00:11:47,840
Ayuh.

232
00:12:13,480 --> 00:12:14,250
Dewa agung.

233
00:12:14,840 --> 00:12:16,250
Saya dah kumpulkan tentera syaitan

234
00:12:16,330 --> 00:12:17,480
mengikut pesanan awak.

235
00:12:18,130 --> 00:12:19,480
Asalkan Wu Huan buat sesuatu,

236
00:12:20,080 --> 00:12:23,210
kita isytiharkan peperangan
terhadap Puak Betara dengan segera.

237
00:12:25,330 --> 00:12:26,130
Usah cemas.

238
00:12:26,520 --> 00:12:28,960
Mu Guang ingin pergunakan awak
untuk cari Cemeti Bulan Ungu

239
